the committees began hearings on monday on 13 ryzhkov aides and 
more than 50 ministers in an exercise of the new powers they gained 
under gorbachevs political reforms 
the 542member supreme soviet is to meet for 40 days to confirm 
the appointees and begin drafting legislation 
